|--------|------|----------|
| [GitHub Issue #177](https://github.com/conductor-is/brain/issues/177) | Primary | 2026-03-28 |
| [Sandbox Agent Skills Config](https://sandboxagent.dev/docs/skills-config) | Official docs | 2026-03-28 |
